{{Infobox person | name = Vincent Paronnaud | image = Winshluss.jpg | alt = | caption = Vincent Paronnaud (2009) | birth_name = | birth_date = {{birth year and age|1970}} | birth_place = [[La Rochelle]], [[France]] | death_date = | death_place = | nationality = French | other_names = | occupation = Comic artist, filmmaker | years_active = | known_for = | notable_works = }}
'''Vincent Paronnaud''' (born 1970), a.k.a. '''Winshluss''', is a [[French people|French]] [[comics artist]] and [[filmmaker]].
Paronnaud was born in [[La Rochelle]]. He is French comic book writer and artist. His works comprise one shots: ''Super negra'' (1999), ''Monsieur Ferraille'' (2001), ''Pat Boon'' (2001), ''Welcome to the Death Club'' (2002), ''Smart monkey'' (2002), ''Cornélius ou l'art de la mouscaille et du pinaillage'' (2007), ''Pinocchio'' (2008), ''Flip et Flopi 1996 1998'', ''In God We Trust'' (2013) and ''Les fées - An electric story'' (2014), as well as comic book series ''(AUT) Winshluss'' (2004-2014) and ''Wizz et Buzz'' (2006-2007).<ref>http://www.bedetheque.com/auteur-3718-BD-Winshluss.html</ref>
Paronnaud is best known for cowriting and codirecting with [[Marjane Satrapi]] the highly acclaimed animated film ''[[Persepolis (film)|Persepolis]]'' (2007), for which they received numerous awards including the [[Jury Prize]] at the [[2007 Cannes Film Festival]]<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/4434938/year/2007.html |title=Festival de Cannes: Persepolis |accessdate=2009-12-20|work=festival-cannes.com}}</ref> as well as an [[Academy Award]] nomination for [[Academy Award for Best Animated Feature|Best Animated Feature]].<ref>{{cite press release | title = 80th Academy Awards Nominations Announced | publisher = [[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] | date = 2008-01-22 | url = http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2008/08.01.22.html | accessdate = 2008-02-11}}</ref>
==Awards== * "[[Cinema for Peace]] Award 2008 for Most Valuable Movie of the Year" for ''[[Persepolis (film)|Persepolis]]'' by Vincent Paronnaud and Marjane Satrapi. * [[3rd Globes de Cristal Award|Globe de Cristal for Best Film]] for ''[[Persepolis (film)|Persepolis]]'' in 2008 * Prize for best album for Winshluss's ''Pinocchio'', 2009 Festival International de la Bande Dessinée, [[Angoulême]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bdangouleme.com/49-palmares-2009-fauve-dor-prix-du-meilleur-album |title=Palmarès officiel 2009—Fauve d'or: Prix du meilleur album |accessdate=2009-03-09 |publisher=Festival International de la Bande Dessinée |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305044152/http://www.bdangouleme.com/49-palmares-2009-fauve-dor-prix-du-meilleur-album# |archive-date=2009-03-05 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> * [[Noor Iranian Film Festival]] award in 2013 for Best Animation Director, shared with Marjane Satrapi, on ''[[Chicken with Plums (film)|Chicken with Plums]]''
